These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, golf, ice-hockey, volleyball
There are 4 different nationalities: german, brazilian, malaysian, mexican
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the malaysian##1
5. the mexican is between the brazilian and the malaysian##2
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | volleyball | rowing     | ice-hockey | golf |
| Nationality     | german     | malaysian | mexican  | brazilian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, dressmaker, architect, security-guard
City: colone, new-york, edinburgh, prague
1. the dressmaker is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the far left or far right##3
3. the security-guard is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
5. the architect is on the far right##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Job   | project-manager | dressmaker    | security-guard     | architect  |
| City     | colone    | edinburgh | new-york | prague |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, orchid, zinnia
City: miami, prague, liverpool, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
2. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Flower   | iris   | orchid   | bellflower  | zinnia |
| City           | prague | paris | liverpool | miami  |

