.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, go, snooker
There 4 different types of food: pear, apple, peas, lettuce
1. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing snooker is between the person playing backgammon and the person eating peas##2
3. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
4. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
6. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Game         | billiard | backgammon | snooker | go  |
| Food   | apple  | pear   | lettuce  | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, cycling, soccer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, jazz, blues, trance
1. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | lacrosse    | handball   | cycling | soccer    |
| Music-Genre      | jazz | reggae | blues       | trance |

