.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, chestnut, green, apricot
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, october, august, february
1. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes green##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who likes green##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who likes white##2
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Color    | white | green | apricot | chestnut |
| Birthday   | october | may  | august    | february  |

