.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, musical, spy, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, rugby, snowboarding, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching documentary movies##2
5. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching documentary movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | documentary | spy | musical     |
| Sport     | parkour | badminton  | rugby   | snowboarding |

