.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
House: modern, tower, cottage, victorian
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, skateboard, scooter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the cottage house##1
2. the victorian house is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the victorian house is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the victorian house is on the left of the cottage house##1
5. the modern house is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| House         | victorian | cottage | modern | tower   |
| Transport   | jet-ski | skateboard | helicopter      | scooter |

