.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, japanese, indian, colombian
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, sunflower, amaryllis, dahlia
1. the japanese is on the left of the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the colombian##1
4. the canadian is on the left of the japanese##1
5. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the japanese is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growslily##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality     | canadian | japanese   | indian      | colombian      |
| Flower   | sunflower     | amaryllis | lily | dahlia |

