.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, security-guard, nurse, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, 7up
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the nurse is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
3. the security-guard is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the police-officer is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Job   | dancer | security-guard | nurse      | police-officer   |
| Beverage   | milk  | hot-chocolate    | fanta | 7up |

