.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
House: gothic-revival, art-deco, palace, wooden
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, whist, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing art-deco is the palace house##1
4. the palace house is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
5. the person playing art-deco is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
6. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| House       | gothic-revival | palace | wooden    | art-deco      |
| Game   | whist       | art-deco       | canasta | monopoly |

