.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, cycling, surfing, tennis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, swisher, fonseca, bongani
1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Sport   | lacrosse     | cycling  | tennis | surfing |
| Cigar     | chaman | bongani | swisher     | fonseca    |

