.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, soy-milk, lemonade
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, august, october
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
4. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | soy-milk  | lemonade | iced-tea |
| Birthday           | august     | october | april    | january     |

