3. the person eating cucumber is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
6. the person who's sport is badminton is the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Food         | cucumber | lime | cranberry | cabbage |
| Sport   | weightlifting     | parkour       | volleyball   | badminton      |

