2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | march | december | october | august |
| Hobby         | cooking  | skydiving   | photography | dancing     |

