.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, august, april, november
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, fuchsia, red, blue
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Birthday      | february | august    | november  | april |
| Color   | pink       | fuchsia | red | blue  |

