.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, white, red, purple
There 4 different types of food: papaya, kiwi, lettuce, apricot
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
2. the person who likes white is the person eating apricot##1
3. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
4. the person who likes purple is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating lettuce is between the person who likes purple and the person eating apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Color   | red | white  | fuchsia  | purple |
| Food           | papaya    | apricot | lettuce | kiwi |

