.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea, water, mirinda
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, go, scrabble
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
3. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda        | sprite       | water   | iced-tea |
| Game    | scrabble | go | backgammon | domino  |

