.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, reggae, folk
There are 4 different nationalities: british, thai, french, canadian
1. the french is on the far right##1
2. the canadian is the canadian##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the canadian##3
4. the british is on the far left or far right##3
5. the canadian is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the british is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the french##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | dubstep     | reggae          | folk |
| Nationality      | british | thai | canadian | french  |

 